"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Well <font_kind=yakuza_italic>that's</font_kind> an interesting message.\r\nNo idea where she is, though. It's gotta be a prank."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "This \"Reiko\" though... I can't say I'm not curious.\r\nWish I knew where she was..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "It's her again.\r\nMaybe I should go give her some company."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "If only I could tell where she was..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Looks like she's on the move again.\r\nStill alone too, from the sounds of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "I wish I knew where she was..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Dammit, she already moved again?\r\nShe'll be mine this time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Hey there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Finally. I've been waiting, big boy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "H-Here I am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "You're even hotter than I was expecting.\r\nI guess this means you saw my posts?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Yeah... That's how I ended up here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Mmmm...\r\nSo, you wanna do it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Let's go. I can't wait any longer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "My, you're like a wild animal. <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nBy the way... mind telling me your name?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna eat you up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "You hungry for some of this? In that case...\r\nwhy don't you tell me <font_kind=yakuza_italic>just</font_kind> how tasty I look? <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "W-Well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "You're so cute when you're flustered.\r\nAnyway... what's your name?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "This feels kinda weird.\r\nAre you sure this isn't some kind of trap?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Huhhh? Whaddya mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "I mean, like blackmail. Am I wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Of course you are. Calm down, big guy.\r\nYou get cold feet now that we're finally together?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "You don't need to be nervous.\r\nLet's just relax... like only adults can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Hey, by the way...\r\nyou mind telling me your name?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "My name...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "You don't need to know that.\r\nRight now we're just man and woman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "But... it'll really get me going\r\nif I can call you by your name. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "What do you mean...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "I wanna have something to scream\r\nwhen we're doing it... Is that so bad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "It's Makoto Date."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Date-san? That's a great name.\r\nCome on, Date-san. Tell me you love me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "It's Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san? That's a great name.\r\nCome on, Kiryu-san. Tell me you love me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Tell you what...? Why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "I'm too embarrassed to ask again.\r\nBut... <font_kind=yakuza_italic>please</font_kind>? I need to hear you say it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "I love you, Reiko.\r\nI need you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Mmmm, yeah... That feels nice. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "I can't say something if I don't mean it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "So that means..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "But if you don't love me, why'd you\r\nchase me all the way out here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "You <font_kind=yakuza_italic>really</font_kind> thought you were gonna get lucky?\r\nThink again, perv!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Okay, that's good!\r\nI got all the footage I need."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Ya messed up real bad, old man.\r\nThat'll teach ya to go after cute girls online."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "See, it don't get you any action.\r\nJust a healthy servin' of humiliation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "You're a real pro at this, Reiko-san.\r\nI'll get your share to ya later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Sorry about this, Mister.\r\nI had some fun with you<symbol=note_with_outline> Bye now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Now then! If you don't want this shit all over\r\nthe internet, I'm gonna need two million yen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Your wife n' kids're gonna be real sad\r\nwhen they see it. Ya might even lose your job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Thinkin' about it like that, two mil sounds pretty good, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "I get it now.\r\nThis is how these scams work nowadays."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "It's how they're gonna keep workin', too.\r\nEspecially with chumps like you fallin' for it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "I think you're lucky number twenty.\r\nEvery other schmuck's paid their two million."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Sounds like this ruse has gone well for you.\r\nIt ends now, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Unlike me, I'm sure the other guys you tricked\r\nhad no way of deleting the footage from your phone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Paying up was probably their only choice.\r\nI won't go as easily as they did, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "The hell're ya talkin' about, old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Well... I'm gonna get that phone\r\neven if I have to beat it out of you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "You punks are going to pay for trying to scam me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "You got guts, guy. I respect that.\r\nBut only a moron'd try n' fight all of us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Kamurocho's a strange place, though. Every so often,\r\nyou'll find someone <font_kind=yakuza_italic>just</font_kind> moronic enough to do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "You're funny, old man.\r\nNow bring it on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "The hell...? I don't get it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "I want you to delete the video from your phones.\r\nAll the other ones you guys have taken, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Uh, but... those are..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Y-Yessir!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "Okay, they're all gone. I promise.\r\nYou can check if ya want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "I don't need to waste energy on that.\r\nIf you said you did it, you did it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Ah... One more thing, though.\r\nI want you all to smash your phones to bits."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "You heard me. Use a hammer if you need to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "But... then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Can't do it, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "I-I'll do it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "I like the sound of that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "My beautiful phone..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "It's a fitting punishment. Maybe next time\r\nyou'll think twice before you blackmail people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "But damn, though...\r\nI <font_kind=yakuza_italic>knew</font_kind> that Reiko was too good to be true."
msgstr ""

